com.combex.e.edoc
Class ERes

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--com.combex.e.edoc.ERes
class ERes
extends Object

Utility for integrating with javadoc tools and for localization.

Handle Resources. Access to error and warning counts. Message formatting.

Author:
mods by Mark Miller of combex.com subject to the terms of Sun's SCSL license.
See Also:
java.util.ResourceBundle, java.text.MessageFormat
